Reasons why they said “ew”:

  1. Your Grand Exchange doesn’t have Textures. It looks like you followed a Tutorial didn’t do anything else.

  2. Your Staff Crown Icon Sprites have black around them. Your Client specifies a certain color to be transparent; find it and replace your used color with that one.

  3. Why are your blacked maps using a different color?

How to make it transparent

I already told you.
[/quote]
yes u did , but in what file i need to replace it?[/quote]

The actual Sprite. If you’re asking where you can change the default transparency color - It’s probably stuck into your Client class somewhere.
